  "privacy_policy_page_title": "Custimoo Privacy Policy",
  "privacy_policy_effective_date": "Effective Date: 30/04/2025",
  "privacy_policy_title": "Privacy Policy",
  "auth_agree_privacy_policy": "By signing up, you agree to our",
  "privacy_policy_intro": "<p>Custimoo (\"we\", \"our\", or \"us\") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, store, and protect the personal information collected through our white-label customizer solution integrated on third-party websites.</p>",
  "privacy_policy_s1_title": "1. Information We Collect",
  "privacy_policy_s1_content": "<p>When you use a website that integrates our customizer, we may collect the following data:</p><ul><li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, and shipping address.</li><li><strong>User-Uploaded Assets:</strong> Logos, images, and custom artwork.</li><li><strong>Team Roster Data:</strong> Player name, number, and size preferences.</li><li><strong>Authentication Data:</strong> Information derived from JWT tokens if the host website has its own CRM.</li></ul><p>We begin collecting this data as soon as a logged-in customer enters the customizer.</p>",
  "privacy_policy_s2_title": "2. How We Collect Data",
  "privacy_policy_s2_content": "<p>We collect data in two ways:</p><ul><li><strong>Via Integration with Client Systems:</strong> If the host website has its own CRM or login system, user authentication is passed to us via JWT tokens.</li><li><strong>Direct Collection:</strong> If the host website lacks a login system, we collect the necessary data directly through our interface.</li></ul>",
  "privacy_policy_s3_title": "3. Use of Personal Data",
  "privacy_policy_s3_content": "<p>We use the information collected to:</p><ul><li>Power customization features (e.g., save designs, generate previews).</li><li>Manage user accounts and saved designs.</li><li>Facilitate order fulfillment and shipping.</li><li>Improve the performance and reliability of our customizer.</li></ul>",
  "privacy_policy_s4_title": "4. Data Sharing",
  "privacy_policy_s4_content": "<p>We do not share, sell, rent, or disclose your data to any third parties. All data is used solely for the purposes described in this policy.</p>",
  "privacy_policy_s5_title": "5. Data Storage and Security",
  "privacy_policy_s5_content": "<p>All data is securely stored on Amazon Web Services (AWS) servers located in the United States. We employ industry-standard safeguards to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, or destruction.</p>",
  "privacy_policy_s6_title": "6. Data Retention",
  "privacy_policy_s6_content": "<p>We retain user data for as long as it is necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, or as required by applicable law.</p>",
  "privacy_policy_s7_title": "7. Your Rights",
  "privacy_policy_s7_content": "<p>In accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), users may:</p><ul><li>Request access to their data.</li><li>Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data.</li><li>Request deletion of their personal data.</li><li>Object to the processing of their data in certain circumstances.</li></ul><p>To exercise these rights, contact us at: <a href=\"mailto:privacy@custimoo.com\">privacy@custimoo.com</a></p>",
  "privacy_policy_s8_title": "8. Children's Privacy",
  "privacy_policy_s8_content": "<p>Our services are not intended for children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal data from children.</p>",
  "privacy_policy_s9_title": "9. Changes to This Policy",
  "privacy_policy_s9_content": "<p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted with an updated effective date. Continued use of the customizer after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>",
  "privacy_policy_s10_title": "10. Contact Us",
  "privacy_policy_s10_content": "<p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p><p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:privacy@custimoo.com\">privacy@custimoo.com</a></p><p>Address:<br>Custimoo ApS<br>Danneskiold-Samsøes Allé 41<br>1434 Copenhagen<br>DENMARK</p>",
